{"tid":627550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娛樂App遭封殺　網民圍堵文化部","createTime":"2018-04-13T05:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:12:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e42b0852f9b576787fa46c524c5ff6e69bb5fa","tid":627550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:23:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180413/20359925?_ga=2.48287526.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20359925%3F_ga%3D2.48287526.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ae8cef7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20359925%3F_ga%3D2.48287526.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=df89c3ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180413/20359925?_ga=2.48287526.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n娛樂App遭封殺　網民圍堵文化部<br />\n<br />\n3.9K<br />\n兩岸要聞<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180413/large/a1703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180413%2Flarge%2Fa1703a.gif&h=fe6c278e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批網民在文化部外抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共官方封殺熱門娛樂App「內涵段子」所引發的抗議尚未平息，示威熱潮更有遍地開花迹象，社交網站昨流傳全國段友（內涵段子用戶）抗議片段，位於北京的文化部有年輕網民持螢光棒抗議、長沙段友舉手機高喊口號，也有網民大合唱，憑歌寄意控訴軟件被封。抗議聲音在全國各地此起彼落，事件被形容為「六四事件」以來中國最大的上街抗議中共行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n數十公安戒備<br />\n<br />\n隨着段友在廣電總局門前示威後，昨日再有更多各地示威的片段流出，有網民持螢光棒，前晚在文化部前舉橫幅抗議。四川成都網民以車輛響按打死火燈聲援，也有市民拉開「天下段友一家親，段友有難八方支援」的橫額。另有視頻顯示，上百段友到某市的政府廣場聚集，數十名警察到場戒備，透過揚聲器警告聚會及亂響按違法。<br />\n<br />\n也有段友憑歌寄意，大合唱西安歌手王建房改編歌曲《在人間》，歌詞提到「當某天那些夢啊，溺死在人海裏，別難過讓他去，這首歌就當是葬禮」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，各地政府也出招應對，針對段友「一長兩短」的暗號式響按，陝西西安交警警告，凡喇叭音量超過105分貝，連續響按超過兩次，或每次超過0.5秒，司機可被處罰100元人民幣。四川公安廳網絡安全保衞總隊在官微稱，法律規定未經許可的聚集活動涉嫌違法，若然擾亂秩序，可處15日以下拘留及罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTwitter/新浪微博<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180413/large/a1703b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180413%2Flarge%2Fa1703b.gif&h=70e3206d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者持橫額聲援「內涵段子」。"},{"pid":"0077f76d65fded394b9c3e92133c8a15d7559769","tid":627550,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇機會重現坦克碌豬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e65a91749ee237de0f4f0260b055ae97d549d0","tid":627550,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31325e9fbc5b99c36d226d75e346e6be9a2a494f","tid":627550,"uid":37375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:52:11.000Z","msg":"揾個中學生學歷既人治國係咁上下"},{"pid":"27edc00285d0618a5b99d391c522e6c25ba502dc","tid":627550,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"愛國愛黨啦你班死仆街 作咩反？ 冇娛樂你還有黨"},{"pid":"5f643fb1c6d7882e0013f28772e668c640ba6b9e","tid":627550,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母係咪乜都要紅底白字"},{"pid":"eafcd072ee44256acaef26454d0c98fe89487d9e","tid":627550,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"香港居民發左賀電未？"},{"pid":"799994161b51a7132c4c579b50de70e32bc49805","tid":627550,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"寧要核子 不要段子<br />\n明唔明呀支那豬"},{"pid":"690d34785600fdf22c9b60a6468ec6b25b9d2d99","tid":627550,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:01:13.000Z","msg":"出坦克啦<br />\n唔出既話經濟發展唔到"},{"pid":"b25064e94efd2c6b982dc2fe3107c0c366aa5353","tid":627550,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T12:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99a4d40c53e2e3cc8c561459127be7304cbb116","tid":627550,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"為咗娛樂app<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eea8c837ce70fe1b20d7882752c7464972efb5","tid":627550,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"7-1 3+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f515aa2ee8469e3829ba704d9a1b93da095361","tid":627550,"uid":84360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"也有網民大合唱<br />\n係咪唱今天我..."},{"pid":"3abebba9ec7912adbe6dce94f4b03883c243ed00","tid":627550,"uid":61396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T13:41:14.000Z","msg":"本來過幾日<br />\n交完工課就無事<br />\n<br />\n依家就大件事了<br />\n中共最怕哋人集結"},{"pid":"336ec269d5b9e68380e59277e62e0bdb0584a9cd","tid":627550,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"習大大永續冇人出聲，手機app封殺，出嚟搏命，毒撚好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}